title: 2020–21 Eintracht Frankfurt season
text:
The 2020–21 season was the 121st season in the existence of <a href="Eintracht%20Frankfurt">Eintracht Frankfurt</a> and the club's ninth consecutive season in the top flight of <a href="Football%20in%20Germany">German football</a>. In addition to the <a href="2020%E2%80%9321%20Bundesliga">domestic league</a>, Eintracht Frankfurt participated in this season's edition of the <a href="2020%E2%80%9321%20DFB-Pokal">DFB-Pokal</a>. The season covered the period from 7 August 2020 to 30 June 2021.
